    summary: {"cols":["Function","Configured setpoint","Activated at","Backup engaged?","Local / remote OK?"],"rows":2},
    tableLabel: "Data table",
    accept: ["The high-temperature alarm activates at its configured setpoint with correct local and remote signal.","The backup system (if fitted) engages as designed and arrests the temperature rise."],
    note: "On a -80 unit the high-temp alarm and backup are the last line protecting irreplaceable samples - verify both the alarm and that backup actually slows the warm-up, not just that it switches on."
