    pre: ["Buffered (glycol-encased) probes at the in-load / worst-case positions, so readings reflect product mass and ignore brief air spikes.", "Representative sample inventory loaded per the defined pattern; range-rated loggers at worst-case + in-rack positions; pre-study calibration recorded.","Representative period and routine sample-retrieval frequency defined."],
    steps: ["Load the defined inventory and energize per normal operation.","Position loggers at worst-case + in-rack positions; record each S/N.","Program loggers to record at intervals no greater than 5 minutes.","Run over the defined period, performing routine sample-retrieval openings at the realistic frequency.","Stop logging, download data, perform post-study calibration verification.","Identify hottest in-use location, coldest in-use location, and overall mean, and record them in the table."],
