    steps: ["Record the configured high-temp, low-temp, and door-ajar setpoints and delays.","HIGH and LOW temp alarms: drive temperature toward each limit; record activation against the reference, confirm correct routing to local and remote/BMS, record delay.","DOOR-AJAR alarm: hold the door open past the configured delay; confirm activation and signal routing; close and confirm it clears.","Confirm each clears on return to normal and record in the table."],
    summary: {"cols":["Alarm","Configured limit","Activated at","Delay","Local / remote OK?","Pass/Fail"],"rows":3},
