    pre: ["Buffered (glycol-encased) probes at the in-load / worst-case positions, so readings reflect product mass and ignore brief air spikes.", "Representative stock load and traffic profile in place; loggers at in-stock + OQ worst-case zones per the map; pre-study calibration recorded.","Representative period and routine traffic/door-opening pattern defined."],
    steps: ["Load the defined stock per the loading map and operate normally.","Position loggers at OQ-identified worst zones plus in-stock positions; record each S/N.","Program loggers to record at intervals no greater than 5 minutes.","Run over the defined period applying the routine traffic and door-opening pattern; log the openings.","Stop logging, download data, perform post-study calibration verification.","Identify hottest in-use zone, coldest in-use zone, and overall mean, and record them in the table."],
