    steps: ["DOCK DOOR: open the dock door(s) for the defined interval; record the peak deviation and recovery time in the near-door zone.","HVAC FAILURE (if in scope): simulate an HVAC failure per the approved method; record the affected-zone deviation and recovery.","Identify which zones breach the band and for how long.","Record results in the table."],
    attach: "Logger traces of the dock-door and/or HVAC-failure scenarios, annotated.",
