    steps: ["Confirm the representative stock load and operate the warehouse normally.","Position study loggers at the OQ worst-case zones plus representative positions; record each S/N.","Program loggers per the protocol interval; synchronize clocks.","Run over the defined seasonal/worst-case period under live stock and traffic.","Stop logging, download data, perform post-study calibration verification, and compute MKT where required.","Record hottest zone, coldest zone, and overall mean (and MKT) in the table."],
    attach: "Raw and analyzed loaded zone data (seasonal), the loading/zone map, MKT calculations, and pre/post calibration records.",
