    steps: ["With the chamber stable and logging, interrupt power for the defined outage duration.","Record the peak T and RH excursions during the outage.","Restore power and confirm the chamber restarts safely to the study condition without manual intervention (or per design).","Verify the logging/monitoring record handles the gap correctly - the gap is recorded, not silently overwritten or lost.","Record results in the table."],
    attach: "Logger trace and monitoring-system record across the outage, showing gap handling.",
