    pre: ["Buffered (glycol-encased) probes at the in-load / worst-case positions, so readings reflect product mass and ignore brief air spikes.", "Representative sample load per the defined pattern; T and RH loggers at worst-case + within-load positions per the map; pre-study calibration recorded.","Defined period reflecting study use."],
    steps: ["Install the representative sample load and operate at the study condition.","Position T/RH loggers at worst-case + within-load positions (samples affect airflow and local RH); record each S/N.","Program loggers to record at intervals no greater than 5 minutes.","Run over the defined period.","Stop logging, download data, perform post-study calibration verification.","Record the worst-case T and RH positions and the overall T and RH means in the table."],
