    steps: ["Install the representative load and position sample probes at representative and worst-case positions; record S/Ns.","Run the real freezing profile.","At each position, compare the observed profile to the programmed profile.","Confirm all positions follow the temperature/rate requirement within tolerance.","Record the per-position result in the table."],
    attach: "Raw and analyzed loaded freezing-profile data (all positions) and pre/post calibration records.",
