    steps: ["Micronize a representative lot at the qualified grinding/pushing-gas pressures and feed rate.","Sample the milled powder and measure the particle-size distribution (laser diffraction): D10/D50/D90.","Compare D50 and D90 (and span) to acceptance.","Confirm the target PSD at the qualified CPPs.","Record PSD results in the data table."],
