    summary: {"cols":["Attribute","Result","Acceptance","Pass/Fail"],"rows":3},
    tableLabel: "Data table",
    accept: ["Fines/agglomeration and (where relevant) amorphous content are within acceptance.","Confirming milling did not degrade the material."],
    note: "Jet milling imparts mechanical energy that can create amorphous regions (a stability/dissolution risk) and excess fines (a flow/handling risk). For sensitive APIs, amorphous content by XRPD/DSC is a real acceptance attribute, not just size."
