    steps: ["Confirm process yield (collected product vs theoretical) at the qualified CPPs.","Run at the minimum and maximum feed rate/throughput and confirm product attributes (moisture, PSD, amorphous) hold.","Confirm yield and attributes across the throughput range.","Record yield and throughput-range results in the data table."],
